              },
              "free_text": [
                "      Fast reactor spectrum",
                " averaged over energy interval nu-bar values relative",
                " to the nu-bar values at thermal energy."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A fast-reactor spectrum. The energy spectrum is",
                " given in fig. 2 in JNE,27,395,1973 and were calculated",
                " from the zero-dimensional program SPENG.",
                "The measurements were made with three different reactor",
                " cores giving median fission energies for 235U (core",
                " centre) of 50, 170 and 240 keV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "92-U-235",
                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.933
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The fission chamber contains",
                "520 mg of 92-U-235. Isotopic abundances 93.3% U-235",
                "                                     and 6.7% U-238."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "FISCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".A fission chamber similar to those for U-235",
                " and Pu-239 contains a Cf-252 source giving about",
                " 50 spontaneous fissions per minute."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "PART-DET": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "FF",
                "PN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "    Fission fragments and prompt neutrons in",
                " coincidence."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".To obtain a reasonable counting rate, the Pu-239 runs",
                " were made with a higher reactor effect than the U-235",
                " runs. The fission counting rates in the Pu-239 and",
                " U-235 measurements were about 2.5 and 10 fissions per",
                " minute, respectively.",
                ".The time distribution of the background pulses in the",
                " scintillator caused by the reactor was checked. No",
                " time correlation of the background pulses could be",
                " observed."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FLAG": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                3.0
              ],
              "free_text": [
